new.name: Open5GS-CVE-2025-41067-CVE-2025-41068-PoC
new.description: This repository contains the Proof-of-Concept (PoC) exploit scripts for two vulnerabilities, CVE-2025-41067 and CVE-2025-41068. These vulnerabilities affect the NRF (Network Repository Function) component of Open5GS in versions prior to 2.7.6 and can be triggered by an attacker to cause a Denial of Service (DoS).
